# Real Estate Manager Skill

## Overview
Manages tasks, deadlines, and email reminders for two properties.
Data stored in `~/.openclaw/workspace-realestate/properties.json`

## Tree Structure
```
Property (Millpointe, NPlainfield)
  └── Category (Rent, PropertyTax, Maintenance, etc.)
        └── Item (text + DEADLINE:YYYY-MM-DD tag + other tags)
```

## Data File
`~/.openclaw/workspace-realestate/properties.json`

Same fluid tree format as todo-manager. If not exists, initialize with default structure below.

