## Script Helper
```bash
python3 ~/.openclaw/workspace-realestate/skills/realestate-manager/scripts/realestate.py <command> [args]
```

## Operations

### LIST all properties and tasks
`python3 realestate.py list`
Show full tree with deadlines highlighted.

### SHOW upcoming deadlines
`python3 realestate.py deadlines [days]`
Default 30 days. Shows items sorted by DEADLINE date.
Flag 🔴 if within 7 days, 🟡 if within 30 days.

### ADD item
`python3 realestate.py add "Millpointe/Rent" "RENT new item DEADLINE:2026-04-03"`
Auto-creates path if needed.

### MARK done
`python3 realestate.py done "Millpointe/Rent" 1`

### SEND email reminder
`python3 realestate.py email "subject" "body" "to@email.com,partner@email.com"`
Uses Gmail SMTP with App Password from environment variable GMAIL_APP_PASSWORD.
Sender: the configured GMAIL_ADDRESS env var.

### CONFIG emails
Email addresses stored in `~/.openclaw/workspace-realestate/config.json`:
```json
{
  "chuck_email": "chuck@email.com",
  "nisha_email": "nisha@email.com",
  "gmail_address": "sender@gmail.com"
}
```
Read config with: `python3 realestate.py config-show`
Set email: `python3 realestate.py config-set chuck_email chuck@email.com`

### SEND deadline reminders
`python3 realestate.py remind [days]`
Finds all items due within [days] days, sends email to both Chuck and Nisha.
Format: clean list per property.

## Email Format
Subject: `[PropertyName] Reminder: <item> due <date>`
Body:
```
Hi Chuck & Nisha,

Upcoming deadline reminder:

🏠 Millpointe — 392 College Drive
  📅 Mar 3: Monthly rent collection
  📅 Apr 1: Property tax payment

🏠 NPlainfield — 401 Highway
  📅 Apr 1: Property tax payment

— Real Estate Assistant
```

## Rules
- GMAIL_APP_PASSWORD must be set as env var — never hardcode it
- Always confirm before sending emails
- Show preview of email before sending
- If config emails not set, ask user to set them first with config-set